{"tid":2507164,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《尚氣》劉思慕普通話感謝中國粉絲，同時回應黑粉：巴不得我們失敗的人等著吧","createTime":"2021-04-27T23:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T23:45:42.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"37e0ba281a430573879af53574c2bc061f6521e4","tid":2507164,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T23:35:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SimuLiu/status/1386701125840035844?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSimuLiu%2Fstatus%2F1386701125840035844%3Fs%3D09&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0kBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=dc05c2bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSimuLiu%2Fstatus%2F1386701125840035844%3Fs%3D09&h=683451ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SimuLiu/status/1386701125840035844?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漫威超級英雄電影《尚氣與十環傳奇》將於9月3日上映。近日劉思慕在推特上傳影片，用<br />\n中文感謝中國粉絲。他說：「我想跟我們所有的中國粉絲說一下謝謝！謝謝你們的鼓勵，<br />\n你們的支持，我非常感動。」<br />\n<br />\n他同時還回應了黑粉：「對於另外那些人，巴不得我們失敗的那些人，我沒有什麼話好說<br />\n的，你們好好等著吧！」"},{"pid":"d7ecbff7fc4ffe161b8ead39c79d9de5539a3ceb","tid":2507164,"uid":886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T23:38:22.000Z","msg":"3年後仲係度先講嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2cbce5e69459cbef17d29f10882866a8a12854","tid":2507164,"uid":228894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T23:39:04.000Z","msg":"佢仲未知自己衰咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c71bba12c336649f17632ef4a13b468e424ee1","tid":2507164,"uid":78039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T23:40:26.000Z","msg":"中國上到咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi